profile_positions.description:
▪ Digital PR in charge of the relations with bloggers and online media, organizing meetings and educational tours for the promotion of the destination, setting up travel and accommodations arrangements during the educational tours;

▪ Speaker during international trade fairs, online media events, universities seminars and press conferences presenting the field related projects of the Tourist Board: The Social Travel Summit, Hamburg (Germany) 2015 - Social Travel Britain, Salisbury (UK) 2015 - World Travel Market, London (UK) 2012,2013,2014 - The Social Travel Summit, Leipzig (Germany) 2014 - Social Media Tourism Symposium, Rovaniemi (Finland) 2014 - Borsa Internazionale del Turismo Bit, Milan (Italy) 2014 - Nordic Blogger Experience, Helsinki (Finland) 2014 - TTI/TTG, Rimini (Italy) 2013 - University of Bologna, Faculty of Economics, Rimini (Italy) 2013 - Travel Blogger Elevator, Genova (Italy) 2012; TBEX Conference Europe, Girona (Spain) 2012;

▪ Project Manager BlogVille Italy: see project detail in the field below;

▪ Project Manager European Union Relations & Funding for the Tourism Sector.

▪ Travel and Football Event Recruitment Manager Assistant: selection of the staff for different international football youth tournaments in the Cesenatico area in Italy managed by Euro-Sportring, assistant of the Euro-Sportring Event Manager, control and managing of the travel and accommodations arrangements for the different football teams participating at the tournaments in collaboration with the local tourist board;

▪ Interpreter/translator during the international football tournaments;

▪ Interpreter/translator during tourism related workshops and meetings in Italy and Europe for the Tourist Board of Cesenatico.
